<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activate Your Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Rosstech</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Your account has been created, but it needs to be activated before you can log in.</p>
            <p>Please use the following details to log in after activation:</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
            <p><strong>Default Password:</strong> {{defaultPassword}}</p>
            <p>To activate your account, please click the link below:</p>
            <p><a href="{{activationLink}}" class="button">Activate My Account</a></p>
            <p>If the button above does not work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
            <p>{{activationLink}}</p>
            <p>If you did not register for this account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>[Your Company Name] Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
